<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>

<p>Our time sheet management system is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information.</p>

<h3>What Information Do We Collect?</h3>

<ul>
    <li>Name</li>
    <li>Email address</li>
    <li>Phone number</li>
    <li>Job title</li>
    <li>Department</li>
    <li>Time sheet entries</li>
</ul>

<h3>How Do We Use Your Information?</h3>

<ul>
    <li>To manage your time sheet entries</li>
    <li>To communicate with you about your time sheet entries and other work-related matters</li>
    <li>To improve our time sheet management system</li>
</ul>

<h3>How Do We Protect Your Information?</h3>

<ul>
    <li>We use industry-standard security protocols to encrypt and protect data transmission.</li>
    <li>We use secure servers to store your personal information.</li>
    <li>We limit access to your personal information to authorized personnel only.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Do We Share Your Information?</h3>

<ul>
    <li>We do not share your personal information with third parties, except in the following circumstances:</li>
    <li>We may share your personal information with our service providers who assist us in providing our time sheet management system.</li>
    <li>We may share your personal information if required by law or legal process.</li>
</ul>

<h3>How Can You Access or Change Your Information?</h3>

<p>You can access or change your personal information by logging into your account and updating your profile or time sheet entries.</p>

<h3>Contact Us</h3>

<p>If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy or our time sheet management system, please contact us at support@timesheetsystem.com.</p>
